  "body": "### Description\r\nAs part of #3356, we'll need to move away from accessing `Constants` statically.  This will allow us to version constants depending on the current fork.  \r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n* Move all versionable spec-related constants out of `Constants`\r\n* Address all TODOs labeled `TODO(#3394)`\r\n\r\n### In Progress Tasks (check when complete)\r\n- [x] Move `EpochProcessor` into `spec` package, update to use `SpecConstants` internally (@mbaxter)\r\n- [ ] Remove static constants from `data`, `beaconrestapi` (@rolfyone)\r\n- [ ] eth-benchmark-tests (@rolfyone)\r\n- [x] Move `StateTransition` into `spec` package (@mbaxter)\r\n- [ ] Migrate `BlockProcessorUtil` into `spec` package (@mbaxter)",
